headline: Is It Too Late To Consider AutoZone (AZO) After Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Gains?
summary: If you have ever looked at AutoZone and wondered whether the current share price reflects its true value, you are not alone. The stock most recently closed at US$3,522.02, with returns of 2.9% over 7 days, 3.8% over 30 days, 6.6% year to date, 9.1% over 1 year, 51.4% over 3 years and 187.0% over 5 years. This naturally raises questions about where value and risk now stand. Recent news coverage has focused on AutoZone's role as a large US auto parts retailer and its position in the...
